Class SerialisableSoftReference<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.session.SerialisableSoftReference<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type referenced this should be a primitive type or Serializable
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable

    public class SerialisableSoftReference<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Externalizable
    A Serializable wrapper that around a SoftReference. optionally the reference can be forced to null by serialisation to limit the amount of data serialised.
